On last Thursday=E2=80=99s Sharp Tech ( https://sharptech.fm/member/episode=
/disney-vs-charter-and-a-new-espn-reality-the-future-of-the-cable-business-=
risks-for-the-nba-and-other-sports ) we dived deep into the Disney vs. Char=
