nger.com/the-bill-simmons-podcast/2023/9/8/23864072/kansas-city-chiefs-rece=
ivers-ufc-293-espn-million-dollar-picks ) to discuss the same.

As of the time I am writing this Update, the standoff continues, with a Mon=
