Rtg18bCEwc4dW8QbAinlyTNhb1glf_T1-rqF-HPpaP0vn-xyQ ) that SMIC had shipped 7=
nm samples, and Dylan Patel of SemiAnalysis (who I had on for an interview =
last week ( https://stratechery.com/2023/an-interview-with-doug-olaughlin-a=
nd-dylan-patel-about-semiconductors-and-ai/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1=
